===Glyph origin===
{{Han etym}}
{{Han compound|夊|𡕒|ls=ic}} (second character roughly [[ヰ]]) – two feet facing in the same direction. Compare [[⽨]], with feet in different directions (and hence divergent); compare [[夅]], with feet pointing down; compare feet in [[步]]. Compare also footprint in [[夂]], [[夊]], [[𡕒]], and [[韋]].

Note that the left foot has changed shape rather more than the right foot, which still resembles the form in earlier script.

